'''Mir'''是由[[Canonical公司|Canonical公司]]开发的[[Linux|Linux]]操作系统下的显示服务器。原本用以取代[[Ubuntu|Ubuntu]]中的[[X窗口系统|X窗口系统]]<ref name="Ubuntu Wiki">{{cite web |url=https://wiki.ubuntu.com/MirSpec |title=MirSpec – Ubuntu Wiki |publisher=Wiki.ubuntu.com |date= |accessdate=2013-03-06 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130306104754/https://wiki.ubuntu.com/MirSpec |archivedate=2013-03-06 }}</ref><ref name="The H">{{cite web |url=http://www.h-online.com/open/news/item/Canonical-reveals-plans-to-launch-Mir-display-server-Update-1815982.html |title=Canonical reveals plans to launch Mir display server – Update – The H Open: News and Features |publisher=H-online.com |date=2013-02-24 |accessdate=2013-03-06 |archive-date=2013-06-28 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6Hijr1K7z?url=http://www.h-online.com/open/news/item/Canonical-reveals-plans-to-launch-Mir-display-server-Update-1815982.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="Ars Technica">{{cite web |last=Brodkin |first=Jon |url=http://arstechnica.com/information-technology/2013/03/ubuntu-dumps-x-window-system-creates-replacement-for-pc-and-mobile/ |title=Ubuntu dumps X window system, creates replacement for PC and mobile |publisher=Ars Technica |date=2012-05-17 |accessdate=2013-03-06 |archive-date=2013-06-28 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6HijtiAHG?url=http://arstechnica.com/information-technology/2013/03/ubuntu-dumps-x-window-system-creates-replacement-for-pc-and-mobile/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>，但是2017年4月Canonical公司宣佈放棄開發Mir專用的顯示後端服務，並將其開發為以[[Wayland|Wayland]]作為顯示後端的使用者界面<ref>{{cite news|title=Ubuntu Unity is dead: Desktop will switch back to GNOME next year|url=https://arstechnica.com/information-technology/2017/04/ubuntu-unity-is-dead-desktop-will-switch-back-to-gnome-next-year/|publisher=[[Ars_Technica|Ars Technica]]|date=2017-04-06|accessdate=2017-11-11|archive-date=2020-04-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200430044346/https://arstechnica.com/information-technology/2017/04/ubuntu-unity-is-dead-desktop-will-switch-back-to-gnome-next-year/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。並於2017年10月，將原先發佈的版本1.0退回到版本0.28並大幅度的增加對於Wayland的支援程度。<ref>{{cite news|title=Mir 1.0 Is Pulled Back, Now It's Mir 0.28|url=https://www.phoronix.com/scan.php?page=news_item&px=Mir-1.0-Now-Mir-0.28|publisher=[[Michael_Larabel|Michael Larabel]]|date=2017-10-11|accessdate=2018-07-14|archive-date=2018-08-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180823161456/https://www.phoronix.com/scan.php?page=news_item&px=Mir-1.0-Now-Mir-0.28|dead-url=no}}</ref>

==开发==
Canonical公开的Mir开发里程碑：<ref name="Ubuntu Wiki" />
*'''2013年5月''' –  初步完成与[[Unity_Next|Unity Next]]的整合，提供足够的功能以进一步开发完整的桌面系统。
*'''2013年10月''' – Unity Next和Mir与[[Ubuntu_Phone|Ubuntu Phone]]的其余系统完全整合。桌面与笔记本计算机将能够以传统模式使用按需的X系统运行传统的X客户端。
*'''2014年4月''' – 完成与其他的硬件类型的整合。

Ubuntu 13.10含有Mir的安装包，但是由于XMir的不稳定，为了提高用户体验，继续使用X。<ref>{{cite web |url=https://lists.ubuntu.com/archives/ubuntu-devel/2013-June/037401.html |title=Ubuntu graphic stack roadmap update |publisher=Ubuntu |date=2013-06-27 |accessdate=2013-06-28 |archive-date=2020-11-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201111230935/https://lists.ubuntu.com/archives/ubuntu-devel/2013-June/037401.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>14.04 LTS也默认使用X。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.phoronix.com/scan.php?page=news_item&px=MTUxOTQ |title=Ubuntu 14.04 LTS Won't Be Powered By Mir |publisher=Phoronix |date=2013-11-19 |accessdate=2014-02-02 |archive-date=2020-11-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201112030850/https://www.phoronix.com/scan.php?page=news_item&px=MTUxOTQ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

==争议==
Canonical公司在2013年3月4日公开了Mir代替X显示服务器的计划。<ref name="Ubuntu Wiki" />但在此之前，2010年它曾表示将使用[[Wayland|Wayland]]。

